These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: 7up, coffee, lemonade, water
City: colone, nizza, prague, san-francisco
1. City:san-francisco is on the left of Beverage:lemonade##1
2. Beverage:7up is on the left of City:nizza##1
3. Beverage:water is in an odd position##4
4. City:prague is on the left or right of City:san-francisco##3
5. Beverage:7up is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up | coffee | water | lemonade |
| City        | colone | nizza   | san-francisco | prague    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Movie-Genre: crime, musical, scientific, superhero
Birthday: january, august, april, march
1. Movie-Genre:musical is on the left of Movie-Genre:superhero##1
2. Birthday:january is on the left of Birthday:april##1
3. Birthday:april is in an odd position##4
4. Birthday:january == Movie-Genre:crime##1
5. Birthday:august is on the right of Birthday:april##1
6. Birthday:january == Movie-Genre:crime##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | crime  | musical  | superhero |
| Birthday   | march    | january | april | august    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Sport: volleyball, sailing, tennis, ice-hockey
Movie-Genre: animation, documentary, spy, western
1. Sport:ice-hockey is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:western##3
2. Sport:tennis is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:western is on the left or right of Sport:sailing##3
4. Movie-Genre:western is on the right of Movie-Genre:spy##1
5. Movie-Genre:animation is in an odd position##4
6. Sport:sailing is on the right of Sport:tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Sport          | ice-hockey | tennis | sailing    | volleyball      |
| Movie-Genre   | spy        | western     | animation | documentary |

