1. Hobby:drawing is between Beverage:sprite and Beverage:coffee##2
2. Hobby:woodworking is on the left of Hobby:cooking##1
3. Beverage:cola is in an odd position##4
4. Beverage:iced-tea is on the left of Beverage:coffee##1
5. Beverage:iced-tea is on the right of Hobby:cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | woodworking | cooking | drawing | reading |
| Beverage   | cola       | sprite   | iced-tea    | coffee  |

