.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
Sport: handball, rowing, surfing, badminton
Nationality: american, australian, indian, russian
1. Sport:surfing is on the right of Nationality:russian##1
2. Nationality:australian == Sport:badminton##1
3. Nationality:indian is on the right of Sport:handball##1
4. Sport:rowing is on the far left##1
5. Sport:surfing is in an odd position##4
6. Nationality:american is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Sport   | rowing  | handball    | surfing   | badminton       |
| Nationality   | american | russian | indian | australian |

