2. Birthday:january is on the left of Birthday:february##1
3. Movie-Genre:western is on the left of Movie-Genre:mystery##1
4. Birthday:december == Movie-Genre:epic##1
5. Movie-Genre:western is on the left or right of Birthday:february##3
6. Birthday:june is on the right of Birthday:february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | western | mystery | family    |
| Birthday     | december | january  | february     | june |

