.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
Food: cabbage, mango, pepper, watermelon
Transport: jet-ski, bike, roller, quad-bike
1. Food:pepper is on the left or right of Food:cabbage##3
2. Food:cabbage is on the right of Food:mango##1
3. Transport:jet-ski is between Transport:bike and Food:pepper##2
4. Transport:jet-ski is in an odd position##4
5. Food:pepper == Transport:roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | watermelon | mango   | cabbage | pepper |
| Transport    | quad-bike     | bike | jet-ski     | roller  |

