.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
Beverage: 7up, fanta, milk, water
Pet: cat, rabbit, ferret, snake
1. Pet:rabbit is on the far left##1
2. Beverage:milk is on the left or right of Beverage:7up##3
3. Beverage:water is on the far left or far right##3
4. Pet:ferret is on the left of Pet:snake##1
5. Pet:snake is on the right of Beverage:7up##1
6. Pet:ferret is in an even position##4
7. Pet:cat == Beverage:fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | water | 7up    | milk       | fanta |
| Pet       | rabbit  | ferret | snake | cat  |

