.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
Cigar: ritmeester, tiparillo, dunhill, alhambra
Transport: helicopter, jet-ski, subway, van
1. Cigar:tiparillo is in an even position##4
2. Cigar:tiparillo is on the left or right of Transport:helicopter##3
3. Transport:jet-ski is between Cigar:ritmeester and Transport:helicopter##2
4. Cigar:tiparillo is on the far left or far right##3
5. Transport:subway is on the right of Cigar:alhambra##1
6. Transport:subway is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Cigar         | ritmeester | dunhill   | alhambra | tiparillo |
| Transport   | van          | jet-ski | helicopter         | subway  |

 